#

Chickpea and Orange Salad

10 min
$5
250 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-FreeHigh Protein

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Salad

Tags:

HealthyQuickSalad

Description

A refreshing salad combining the zest of oranges with hearty chickpeas, perfect for a light meal or side dish.

Ingredients

  • canned chickpeas: 1 can (15 oz)
  • oranges: 2, segmented
  • red onion: 1/4, thinly sliced
  • fresh parsley: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • lemon juice: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
